{"tid":692184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周六福香港店結業？網民：我真係恭喜你呀","createTime":"2018-06-06T11:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T06:05:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":703,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcb48893b75534753edabf5ad3413cd22bdb0ab","tid":692184,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2085000/2088803/34717874_125621814983330_4585966109286465536_o_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2085000%2F2088803%2F34717874_125621814983330_4585966109286465536_o_1024.jpg&h=3b01a0b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地珠寶店周六福，不少網民都認為是抄襲香港的周大福和六福。盡管感覺山寨，但在 2016 年周六福還是來港開店，其老闆更曾豪言，未來會在香港開足 50 間分店。不過稍早前有網民經過其旺角店，發現已關門大吉，拍下相片相片上載分享，表示：「我真係恭喜你呀。」<br />\n<br />\n對香港網民來說，相信周六福沒有太大好感。稍早前，有網民經過該店，發現已關上鐵閘，閘門外貼出招租告示，看來已經結業，不過暫時未能確定，周六福是否完全撤出香港。<br />\n<br />\n網民看到周六福疑似結業的相片，都紛紛讚好，留言包括：「我除咗講恭喜之外都唔知講乜好，有請小鳳姐出場」，「劣幣被更劣的幣給淘汰了」，「當年搵劉嘉玲剪綵」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2088803/%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E7%A6%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%97%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E6%81%AD%E5%96%9C%E4%BD%A0%E5%91%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2088803%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E7%25A6%258F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%2597%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%2581%25AD%25E5%2596%259C%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2591%2580&d=v3MW6TdbfRbTahejnFT3vQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9b665189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2088803/%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E7%A6%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%97%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%91%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E6%81%AD%E5%96%9C%E4%BD%A0%E5%91%80</a>"},{"pid":"b067f59dc39a3a3fe98f02e9e3270953927a9872","tid":692184,"uid":11962,"like":383,"dislike":2,"score":381,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"連大陸人都唔信既垃圾"},{"pid":"098adf5d9f90b8b7da542819564fde2e8db8e856","tid":692184,"uid":78971,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f824378d292a583db52aeae72a4650e776c76075","tid":692184,"uid":82450,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"98ce5a61dfb74bcf6bb0a2167b3935d2330d3843","tid":692184,"uid":42188,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24f31b35ed5b458d1d80068021bd3749d30bf49","tid":692184,"uid":1977,"like":111,"dislike":15,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/638/99c/63899cf0b5ddb088d2152c88f7e00e12d7d5efd8_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F638%2F99c%2F63899cf0b5ddb088d2152c88f7e00e12d7d5efd8_n.jpg&h=c76e6c9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58a8ec6202eccc069eb51722192432876a0026c1","tid":692184,"uid":39464,"like":190,"dislike":7,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170216/large/1487244829_7675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170216%2Flarge%2F1487244829_7675.jpg&h=90ba8825&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a8776fa10047ce5bb9159b9ff99f9c0b0cc0fe9","tid":692184,"uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":161,"score":-152,"quote":{"pid":"58a8ec6202eccc069eb51722192432876a0026c1","tid":692184,"uid":39464,"like":190,"dislike":7,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img